summary:
ALRIGHT SO THIS IS KIND OF A LONG SHOT THEORY BUT EVERY TIME I THINK ABOUT IT I START TO BELIEVE IT MORE...
So, for Harry’s...
body:
ALRIGHT SO THIS IS KIND OF A LONG SHOT THEORY BUT EVERY TIME I THINK ABOUT IT I START TO BELIEVE IT MORE…

So, for Harry’s Melbourne concert this year, I was able to get barrier and throught the ENTIRE concert I kept making eye contact with H and every now and then he would add a little smile…

Up until now I thought it was because of my terrible dancing or that I barely used my phone and just listened to him sing or the fact that I had a pride flag, BUT THEN I remembered I literally have a very visible paper airplane tattooed on my wrist


AND DO YOU KNOW WHO ELSE HAS A PAPER AIRPLANE TATTOOED ON THEIR ARM ?!?!?
